## 1. Autenticação (`/auth`)

### `GET /auth/pow/challenge`

Gera um desafio Proof-of-Work para anti-bot.

| | |
|---|---|
| **Auth** | ❌ Pública |
| **Response** | `ApiResponse<Map>` |

```json
{
  "data": { "challenge": "a1b2c3d4e5f6..." }
}
```

---

### `POST /auth/signup`

Inicia o cadastro. Valida credenciais e retorna URI do TOTP + backup codes.

| | |
|---|---|
| **Auth** | ❌ Pública |
| **Response** | `ApiResponse<SignupResponseDTO>` |

**Request Body:**
```json
{
  "username": "satoshi",
  "passphrase": "correct horse battery staple ...",
  "challenge": "a1b2c3d4...",
  "nonce": "000042",
  "voucherCode": "KERO-XXXX-XXXX"
}
```

**Response Data:**
```json
{
  "otpUri": "otpauth://totp/Kerosene:satoshi?secret=JBSWY3DP&issuer=Kerosene",
  "backupCodes": ["A1B2C3D4", "E5F6G7H8", "..."]
}
```

---

### `POST /auth/signup/totp/verify`

Confirma o código TOTP para finalizar o cadastro. Retorna JWT.

| | |
|---|---|
| **Auth** | ❌ Pública |
| **Response** | `ApiResponse<String>` (JWT token) |

**Request Body:**
```json
{
  "username": "satoshi",
  "totpCode": "123456",
  "preAuthToken": "<session-id>"
}
```

---

### `POST /auth/login`

Inicia login. Valida password e retorna session ID para fase TOTP.

| | |
|---|---|
| **Auth** | ❌ Pública |
| **HTTP Status** | `202 Accepted` |
| **Response** | `ApiResponse<String>` (session ID) |

**Request Body:**
```json
{
  "username": "satoshi",
  "passphrase": "correct horse battery staple ..."
}
```

---

### `POST /auth/login/totp/verify`

Confirma TOTP no login. Retorna JWT definitivo.

| | |
|---|---|
| **Auth** | ❌ Pública |
| **Response** | `ApiResponse<String>` (JWT token) |

**Request Body:**
```json
{
  "username": "satoshi",
  "totpCode": "123456",
  "preAuthToken": "<session-id>"
}
```

