## Fluxos de Autenticação

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant S as Server
    participant R as Redis

    Note over C,S: Signup Flow
    C->>S: GET /auth/pow/challenge
    S-->>C: challenge string
    C->>S: POST /auth/signup (username + passphrase + PoW)
    S->>R: Salva SignupState
    S-->>C: otpUri + backupCodes
    C->>S: POST /auth/signup/totp/verify (totpCode)
    S-->>C: JWT Token

    Note over C,S: Login Flow
    C->>S: POST /auth/login (username + passphrase)
    S->>R: Salva LoginState
    S-->>C: session ID (202)
    C->>S: POST /auth/login/totp/verify (totpCode)
    S-->>C: JWT Token

    Note over C,S: Passkey Login (bypassa TOTP)
    C->>S: POST /auth/passkey/login/start?username=X
    S-->>C: assertion options
    C->>S: POST /auth/passkey/login/finish (assertion)
    S-->>C: JWT Token
```

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant S as Server
    participant Q as Quorum Peers

    Note over C,S: Internal Transaction
    C->>S: POST /ledger/transaction (JWT + TransactionDTO)
    S->>S: Rate limit check (Redis)
    S->>S: Resolve wallets + verify ownership
    S->>S: TOTP + Passkey verification
    S->>S: Update balance (snapshot)
    S->>Q: Phase 1 PREPARE
    Q-->>S: ACKs (≥2/3)
    S->>Q: Phase 2 COMMIT (await)
    Q-->>S: Commit ACKs
    S->>S: Persist to DB
    S-->>C: 200 OK
```
